  <thing id="cRagS2FaSw" name="Fast Swimmer" description="Starting at 7th level, a freebooter may swim half her speed as a move action or her normal speed as a full-round action with a successful Swim check. The freebooter gains a +2 bonus on Swim checks.{br}{br}This ability replaces woodland stride." compset="ClSpecial">
