  <thing id="abS2RcCamp" name="Razor Coast Campaign" description="For this campaign players will receive built in bonuses based on their levels.  These bonuses help to off-set the fact that its a very low magic campaign.\n\n* You receive 3 bonus Action Points a level.\n* You receive a bonus to AC and saving throws equal to 1/2 your character level.\n* You receive a bonus to all attack and damage rolls qual to 1/3 your character level.\n* When you wear armor or shields you gain a bonus to your touch AC vs guns.\n** +1 for medium armor\n** +2 for heavy armor\n** +1 for any shield" compset="Ability" summary="You recieve bonuses to AC, saves, attack &amp; damage based on your level." uniqueness="useronce">
