  <thing id="atS2PirCha" name="Pirate Charge" description="Your army of pirates is skilled at putting the fear into mundane sailors, provoking stupid mistakes and overconfidence in battle. The target army must attempt a Morale check (DC = 10 + your army&apos;s ACR) at the start of each Melee or Ranged phase; failure means it reduces its OM and DV against your army by 2 for that phase. If the target army succeeds at two of these Morale checks, it&apos;s immune to this tactic for the remainder of the battle." compset="ArmyTactic">
