  <thing id="spRcHeaSti" name="Healing Sting" description="Focusing the power of negative energy, you deal 1d12 points of damage +1 per caster level (maximum 1d12+10) to a living creature and gain an equal amount of hit points if you make a successful melee touch attack. A {i}healing sting{/i} cannot give you more hit points than your full normal total. Excess hit points are lost.\n\n{b}Shadow d20:{/b} Note you do NOT get the damage bonus from your CL to the amount healed by this spell." compset="Spell" summary="Touch deals 1d12 damage +1/level; caster gains damage as hp.">
